FT  08 JAN 94 / UK Company News: Hopkinsons shares fall on warning
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Shares of Hopkinsons Group dipped 5p to 43p yesterday after Mr Bill Goodall,
chairman of the industrial abrasives, plastic products and gas control
equipment group, warned of a pre-tax deficit in the second half.
